                     <interp inst="t18420103-541-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp> for stealing, on the <rs id="t18420103-cd-134" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18420103-541-offence-1 t18420103-cd-134"></join>30th of Decem<lb></lb>ber</rs>, 32lbs. weight of lead, value 4<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18420103-name-755" type="victimName">
